{"tid":1179690,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[準備食草] 香港4月零售貨值按年跌4.5%　遠遜預期","createTime":"2019-05-31T09:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T02:39:32.000Z","uid":73883,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"462e8b23cd848d71e05a0cd545d659024b0ee838","tid":1179690,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T09:35:52.000Z","msg":"統計處公布最新零售業銷貨額數字。2019年4月香港零售業總銷貨價值臨時估計為377億港元，[red按年跌4.5%，差過預期跌0.2%。首4個月合計則下跌2%。[/red]<br />\n<br />\n扣除其間價格變動後，2019年4月的零售業總銷貨數量按年下跌5%。首4個月合計的零售業總銷貨數量的臨時估計下跌2.3%。 <br />\n<br />\n按零售商主要類別的銷貨價值的臨時估計由高至低分析，珠寶首飾、鐘錶及名貴禮物的銷貨價值按年下跌11.4%。其次為服裝下跌2.2%；藥物及化妝品跌6%；百貨公司貨品跌4.3%。 <br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，零售業銷售表現在4月持續疲弱，銷售額的按年跌幅擴大，反映在外圍不確定因素下消費情緒依然審慎，但也部分是由於內地勞動節假期較遲出現(今年在5月初，而去年橫跨在4至5月之間)，導致旅客人數按年增長顯著減慢。"},{"pid":"b62a63e9fd6236295fb1bb71646558e628bbdf2f","tid":1179690,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T09:36:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190531/mobile/bkn-20190531163054547-0531_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190531%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190531163054547-0531_00842_001.html&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoCLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=91e1984b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190531/mobile/bkn-20190531163054547-0531_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c18b27798af04582c1b2d60d574943dbaa57df76","tid":1179690,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T09:37:19.000Z","msg":"驚閪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55354df0e81a6aa687df2d208ade8d06531b19c4","tid":1179690,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T09:37:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cfabdfa8197e9c753921320678c2ed005cbf62e2","tid":1179690,"uid":73883,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05